'''Advanced International Model Higher Secondary School''' is a school in Nepal. It is located in the near busy market of Lagankhel Bus Park, Lalitpur. The school celebrated its [[Silver Jubilee]] in 2016 as it has completed 25 years of establishment. The school has its own [[AIMS International College]] giving master level education .<ref>http://aims.edu.NP</ref>
